ality and security of the Covered Services; to contact or cooperate with law enforcement regarding actual or suspected CSAM, NCM, or illegal Content; or to comply with any applicable law, regulation, or court order; and 8. Training of all of Defendants’ employees upon hire or within one hundred and twenty (120) days after entry of this Order, and at least once every twelve (12) months for employees with access to Covered Information, on how to safeguard Covered Information;

